OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGreen energy projects worth
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbillions stuck on hold     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,6,FBillions of pounds' worth of green     
OL,7,Fenergy projects are on hold because    
OL,8,Fthey cannot plug into the UK's         
OL,9,Felectricity system, BBC research shows.
OL,11,FSome new solar and wind sites are      
OL,12,Fwaiting up to 10 to 15 years to be     
OL,13,Fconnected because of a lack of capacity
OL,14,Fin the system - known as the "grid".   
OL,16,FRenewable energy companies worry it    
OL,17,Fcould threaten UK climate targets.     
OL,19,FNational Grid, which manages the       
OL,20,Fsystem, acknowledges the problem but   
OL,21,Fsays fundamental reform is needed.     
